## Documentation Expectations

| Document | Update trigger |
|----------|---------------|
| `README.md` | Any change to setup, env vars, or scripts |
| `docs/architecture.md` | New infrastructure, layer changes, new patterns |
| `docs/api-contract.md` | Any new endpoint or changed response shape |
| `docs/ways-of-working.md` | Process or convention changes |
| `docs/adrs/` | Any significant decision (see above) |
| `packages/shared-types` | Any API response change |

Documentation PRs do not need a ticket, but they do need a reviewer.

